//3.update all prices with 2% of its original price
mysql> update Product set price=price+(price*2/100);
Query OK, 5 rows affected (0.00 sec)
Rows matched: 5  Changed: 5  Warnings: 0

mysql> select*from Product;
+-----+--------+-------+
| pid | pname  | price |
+-----+--------+-------+
